  dialogue:
  - "Rivera: Yes! Thank you Director. I\u2019ll get the best cleaners and do our
    best.\n\nGood luck Parker! Sorry that we couldn\u2019t do both...\n\nParker:
    I don\u2019t agree on this but will make one last sweep while the cleanup crew
    arrives to do my best regardless."
  - "Allocated 25 workers to Ecologist Rivera\u2019s cleanup team."
